  <brief_title>Biological Factors Predicting Response to Chemotherapy in Advanced Non Small Cell Lung Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>Biological Factors Predicting Response to Chemotherapy in Advanced Non Small Cell Lung Cancer : a Prospective Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
